      "text": "Deews irr weenuu Wahr-\ndu runnajs/ to eſimu es diwi-\nkahrt dsirdejs/ ka Deews war-\nrens trr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tu ak KUNGS! eſi\nſchehligs/ jo tu makkati ikkurain\npehz fawa Darba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es peeminnu tevis gulleht\needanis/ un usmohsdancees doh-\nmaju es no tewin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tu eſi man par Pali-\ngn/ un appakſch tawu Spahr-\nnu Ehnas dseedu es preezigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Manna Dwehfefe tevim\npeekerrahs/ tawa labba Rohka\nmann atspeesch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet winni/ kas mannu\nDwehfeli mekie ispohſtibt/ no-\ngrims patchôs Seimnes Dsit-\nkumôs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee taps zaur Sohbinu\nfamaitati/ un buhs Lapſahn\npar Barribu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tas Kehntnsch prec-\nzafees ceſſch Deewa/ kas pee ta\nſwehre/ tas leelifees/ jo to Mel-\nkutu Mutte taps aisbahſta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta LXIII. Dseeima.\nIrr weena gauscha Guhdſefhana Dahwida/\nka wiꞥſch fawas Nelaimibas pehz to Dee-\nwa Nammu un Kristitu Draudsi ne warrus\npeemekleht: 2. Luhds/ Deews gribbetu\nwinnam attaf palihdseht: 5. Tab grib\nwiꞥſch par to pateikt: 7/8. Wehl teem Ee-\nnaidneekeem/ lai tee pohtâ eet: 10.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Fena Dahwida Dseeſ-\nma/ kad wiꞥſch eekſch\njuhda Tuksneses bja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ak Deews! tu eſi mans\nSTIPRAJS DEEWS/ te-\nwis mekleju es paschâ Rihtâ/\npehz tewis flahpst untannai Dweh-\nfelei/ pehz tewis ilgojahs mannai\nMeefat/ tantâ un iſkaltufchâ\nSeimnê/ kur Uhdens newaid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Skattiht tawu Spehku\nun tawu Gohdu/ jo ta eſimu es\ntewi fwehtâ Weetâ redſejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tawa Schehlastiba irr\nabbaka/ ue ka Dshwiba/ man-\nnas Luhpas tewi flawe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tur gribbetu es tewi teikt\nmuhſcham/ un mannas Rohkas\neekſch tawa Wahṛda pazelt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas buhtu mannai Dweh-\nfelei/ itt ka kad winna ar Tan-\numeem un Bahrdumeem pa-\nchdinata taptu/ kad manna\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta LXIV. Dseeima.\nIrr weena luhdsama Dseeima Dahwida/ ka\nDeews winna Aprunnatajus gribbetu no-\nmaitaht: 2. Wehl un fluddina teem to\ngalleju Samaitafchannu: 8.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Fena Dahwida Dseeſ-\nma/ preekſch ta augsta\nDseedataja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Klaust ak Deews! mannu\nBalfi/ kad es schehlojoſs/ pafar-\ngi niannu Dshwibu nó to Ge-\nnaidneeku Breetimbas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Apslep manu no to Launu\npatlehpteem Padohmeem/ no to\nLaunadarritajn Trakfofchanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas fawas Mehles trinn/\nka Sohbinu/ un uswelk (to\nStohpu)/ winnu Bultas irr\nruhkti Wahṛdi.\n"
    }
  ],
